INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('123', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">时尚这种东西没有什么标准，原始人用树皮枝叶做的衣服算不算时尚，到了石器时代，有了骨针，他们学会用兽皮做衣服防寒，</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"640\" height=\"859\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190811/1565493179545236.jpg\"/></p><p><span class=\"breakVideo-close\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 50px; width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这算不算时尚，到了唐朝，发明了连衣裙而且以胖为美，那么杨贵妃算不算时尚。到了民国时期，上海滩里的方艳云，一袭旗袍，红遍整个上海滩，算不算时尚。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"640\" height=\"859\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190811/1565493179459241.jpg\"/></p><p><span class=\"breakVideo-close\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 50px; width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">毛利人的服装、纹身和战舞算不算时尚？在特定的时期特定的地点都算。好比现在，以高瘦和气质为美的时代，很多人都会选择紧身装来凸显自己的身材，因为紧身装和这个时代的主流审美是有很大关联的。</p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"640\" height=\"829\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190811/1565493217986126.jpg\"/></p><p><a style=\"outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 100px; height: 100px;\"></a></p><p><span class=\"breakVideo-close\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 50px; width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过这样给人的感觉是重心太低，整个人看起来宽扁，只要厚实的一堆，没有高挑的气质，于是设计师们在牛仔裤的臀部、膝盖处和脚踝处做了小处理，让臀部更紧俏，。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"640\" height=\"889\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190811/1565493217155628.jpg\"/></p><p><span class=\"breakVideo-close\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 50px; width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">膝盖的中间点更加修长，而裸露的脚踝，给人的感觉就是这个人的身材太高了，裤子看起来反而更短，强烈的视觉效应形成增高的效果，虽然紧身牛仔裤是为了显高显瘦而设计，但是要有一点点微胖穿起来才会更美丽</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"640\" height=\"881\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190811/1565493217849663.jpg\"/></p><p><span class=\"breakVideo-close\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 50px; width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">紧身牛仔裤就是顺应这样的审美要求进行了进一步的改良，以前的牛仔裤较为宽松，针对肥胖人群，还有专门加肥加大的牛仔裤。</p><p><br/></p>', '1565493225', '7');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('124', '<article><p class=\"info\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: gray; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\"></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190812/1565570222797791.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>大家好！今天就来给大家分享一组街拍，到底是什么样的，就让我们一起来看一看吧。互联网时代，我们只要拿着手机就可以看看世界各种各样的事情，中国，朝鲜，美国，印度，日本等等，有的让我开心，有的让我们悲伤，有的让我们值得去学习，有的给我们深深的感动，互联网让我们生活变得快捷高效，让我们看见不一样的世界，让我们与人们交流变得方便。无论做什么已经离不开互联网了，只要手机在手可以和小姐姐聊天，看看美女，男子女子都可以，甚至是网友，无疑是生活变得更加方便了。路人街拍：多肉版辣妈穿简约装，牛仔裤多出一条“腰带”，真时尚</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190812/1565570222198299.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190812/1565570222575256.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190812/1565570222852620.jpg\"/></p></article><p><span class=\"rbtn\">举报</span></p><p><br/></p>', '1565570237', '7');
