color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上海气象主播沙柏宁前往洋山港追风<br/>结果被风吹得头发凌乱<br/>脸都变形了……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p2.qhimg.com/t01795e6a2233b00763.gif\" alt=\"t01795e6a2233b00763.gif?size=324x256\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随后，<br/>他自己也在微博中晒出了<br/>出发前和追风后的样子，<br/>对比非常明显了...</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p8.qhimg.com/t0191c4b1778405a20f.jpg\" alt=\"t0191c4b1778405a20f.jpg?size=476x321\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面这位浙江的记者，<br/>风雨中根本站不住jio</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.qhimg.com/t01ac2c27e3e85dcacf.gif\" alt=\"t01ac2c27e3e85dcacf.gif?size=400x226\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">记者大哥：<br/>“浪可以打到这种程度<br/>头一次也让我这个180斤体重<br/>感觉也有点压不住了！”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p8.qhimg.com/t015724bd4a03d4244c.gif\" alt=\"t015724bd4a03d4244c.gif?size=300x273\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">再来看看新民晚报的新媒体记者直播出镜5分钟全身湿透<br/>胸前那个红色的，<br/>不说还真不知道是雨衣...</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.qhimg.com/t01c4882ca45fc38edd.gif\" alt=\"t01c4882ca45fc38edd.gif?size=356x200\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">浙江各路记者用镜头纪录“利奇马”：<br/>现在风力已经达到了15到16级<br/>确实已经站不稳了！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.qhimg.com/t01b6aec6d9f4ac9074.gif\" alt=\"t01b6aec6d9f4ac9074.gif?size=396x225\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">和其他记者不同<br/>下面这位“台风专用记者”<br/>在风中显得非常淡定——<br/>新京报的记者俞金旻<br/>凭借傲人的体重“独霸”外滩，<br/>成为了网友心目中的“台风专用记者”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p7.qhimg.com/t015401ed69e2488c38.jpg\" alt=\"t015401ed69e2488c38.jpg?size=1080x608\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今天外滩都是我一个人承包了<br/>感觉还是比较自豪吧</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p6.qhimg.com/t01dd69163a50d67bda.jpg\" alt=\"t01dd69163a50d67bda.jpg?size=1080x608\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p6.qhimg.com/t0146622622b109c72d.jpg\" alt=\"t0146622622b109c72d.jpg?size=1080x608\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">来源:新京报<br/>网友评论：<br/>摄像大哥才是最猛的吧</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p5.qhimg.com/t01f8c1f9ad52f030dc.jpg\" alt=\"t01f8c1f9ad52f030dc.jpg?size=416x476\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这些一线记者镜头的记录下，<br/>我们也看到了在台风中<br/>有这样一群人<br/>他们不顾个人安危<br/>全力守护群众的生命财产安全<br/>↓<br/>