INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('216', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果这世界上有一种服装无论昂贵与否，都可以让广大女性为之疯狂的话，那它就应该是婚纱了吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950666259199.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了留下曾经相爱的时光很多的新人情侣们都喜欢在结婚纪念日的时候在拍摄几张婚纱照，为了在老去的时候能跟着爱人坐在一起看着曾经的美好，而不是记忆就这么的匆匆而去什么都没有留下来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950666441155.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以，婚纱对很多女性来说不只是一件衣服，更像是一种承诺，一种对爱的承诺。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950667876376.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950667427580.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这世界上贵重的东西有很多，但是曾经的回忆却是无价的。而如果能在结婚的时候拍一组美丽的婚纱照，估计很多人也就没有遗憾了。大家都喜欢怎样的婚纱呢？欢迎在评论区留言讨论哦！</p><p><br/></p>', '1565950667', '5');
